Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎全速掉头中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一次攻击很快就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俩舷全速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船长 玛雅在那艘船上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的鱼雷 目的不是攻击敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了"击沉"巴鲁丹诺斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的鱼雷...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从鱼雷的路线确认敌舰的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2号3号 装填"沙鱼"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认鱼雷音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离鱼雷命中目标 7秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4 3
