Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,9...90？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他们撞个满怀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦 小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认敌舰锅炉音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前进路线是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锅炉音增大 在上浮中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎全速 俩舷掉头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何后退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想撞翻这艘舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俩舷全速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我撞！
